#ROOMS
#25000
Entrance to the Shotokan Temple~
You have reached the legendary temple of 'Gouken' and his followers. Here
you will view his fellow monks in the ritual fashion they engage in
every day of their lives. The worship of 'Gouken' is very sacred by these
people and therefore urge those that are here for a more 'chaotic' purpose
to leave this place at once.
~
