The Main Gates of the Shotokan Temple~
The gates seem to made of solid gold or some substance similar to gold.
They glisten in the sun reflection and the light from them is almost blinding.
You stand afoot in front of temple, which you can tell from here, is heavy
guarded for intruders.
~
